{
  "texts": [
    "For the primary screening step, 109 studies were left after the other studies were eliminated according to the keywords, titles, and abstracts.",
    "It is also possible to reduce these studies to 52 studies by properly implementing the inclusion and exclusion criteria.Vital information was extracted from each document, categorized and examined.",
    "The year of publication, authors, citation measure, area of study, model, measurement parameters, and dataset were among the details from the paper that were included in this.",
    "Each research was also examined in light of the kind of learning strategy that was employed.",
    "In order to organize this data, we first looked over each paper's title, abstract, and introduction, which usually included all the relevant information."
  ]
}